creator: TeleNitro
descriptionHtml:
صراع الملوك هي لعبة حرب RTS RPG جديدة استراتيجية متعددة اللاعبين تضع جيشك في مواجهة الأصدقاء والأعداء في جميع أنحاء العالم في معركة على البلدان والمدن. هل لديك ما يلزم لسحق أعدائك في معركة PVP عبر الإنترنت؟
قم ببناء مدن ضخمة وشارك في معارك MMO عبر الإنترنت في لعبة صراع الملوك الكلاسيكية. وقم بتعزيز وبناء مدينتك بحيث تكون قوية بما يكفي للدفاع عن نفسها ضد الغزاة الأشرار والجيوش الأخرى.
هل أنت مستعد للانضمام إلى الآلاف من اللاعبين الآخرين في حرب صراع الملوك؟ قم بتجهيز جيشك وحارب الأعداء وقم بإدارة موارد مدينتك لتصبح أحد أقوى اللاعبين على الإطلاق في لعبة صراع الملوك!

خصائص لعبة صراع الملوك:

*لعبة استراتيجية حربية قيادية
- سيحصل أفضل خبير إستراتيجي حربي على جوائز في كل أسبوع.

*قم ببناء مدينتك واستعد للإثارة
- أنت لا تعرف متى سيكون عليك القتال ضد اللاعبين الآخرين. تحتاج مدينتك إلى جيش قوي وأن تكون محمية جيداً في المعركة. قم ببناء مدينتك و بترقية قلعتك وثكنات الجيش والمستشفى وبقية أقسام المدينة للدفاع عن نفسك في معارك PVP متعددة اللاعبين. هل أنت مستعد للحرب؟

*معارك وحروب مع لاعبين متعددين عبر الإنترنت
- أنت لست الشخص الوحيد الذي يبني إمبراطورية ! العب PVP عبر الإنترنت ضد الآلاف من اللاعبين الآخرين في أفضل لعبة MMO إستراتيجية حالياً. تحدى الحصار بتشييد مدينتك أو امبراطوريتك. أرسل جيشك للسيطرة على مدن أخرى.

*عالم MMO مع معارك ملحمية عبر الإنترنت
- قم بالدخول إلى عالم رائع على الإنترنت حيث تتصارع الممالك والامبراطوريات للسيطرة على عالم خيالي. لعبة MMO RPG التكتيكية تجعلك تبني مملكة وتجهز جيش وتجمع الموارد. العب بطريقتك الخاصة في هذه اللعبة القتالية متعددة اللاعبين عبر الإنترنت.

*بناء تحالفات قوية مع الآخرين
- بناء تحالفات مع ملوك وقادة آخرين حول العالم. صراع الملوك هي لعبة RTS MMO RPG على الإنترنت تجعلك قائد للجيش. انضم إلى التحالفات لتساعد نفسك والآخرين. انضم إلى قادة الجيش المتشابهين معك في التفكير وساعدوا بعضكم البعض في بناء المدن أو ترقية المباني أو محاربة جيوش العدو. في هذه اللعبة الإستراتيجية يمكن لتحالفاتك أن تقويك أو تضعفك.

*استراتيجية الوقت وإدارة الموارد
- الجيش القوي يحتاج إلى طعام ومسكن. قم ببناء المزارع والمناجم لكسب الموارد لتقوية مدينتك وجيشك. اربح عملات معدنية مقابل كل مهمة مكتملة وموارد من كل حصاد. قم ببناء دفاعات لمدينتك من مواردك.

*معارك MMO ثلاثية الأبعاد المذهلة
- قم بقيادة جيشك عبر الإنترنت إلى عالم ضخم مليئ باللاعبين وبرسومات ثلاثية الأبعاد. شاهد المعركة بشكل واقعي وتمتع بالتأثيرات الموجودة فيها.

كلما تطورت إمبراطوريتك زاد عدد أعدائك. سيحاول الأعداء الآخرون تحطيم مدينتك وقوتك في لعبة الحرب هذه RTS PVE و PVP MMO. كن دائمًا مستعدًا للإثارة خلال مسير الجيش في المعركة من أجل الدفاع عن أرضك أو للاستيلاء على أرض لاعب آخر.

هل أنت مستعد لتكون قائد لمدينتك؟
ابدأ في بناء مدينتك وقيادة جيشك إلى معارك إستراتيجية ملحمية متعددة من خلال اللعب في لعبة صراع الملوك
قم بتنزيل لعبة صراع الملوك وانضم إلى حرب MMO PVP!

title: صراع الملوك : الغرب

creator: Vplay Games LTD.
descriptionHtml:
This is the western kingdom!
Are you strong enough to roll your kingdom and defeat other players around the world?
It’s time to Proof your strength and abilities!
become one of the most potent players in western kingdoms!

Western kingdoms features!

* strategy competitions!
- be the best strategist and get prizes every week.

* be always ready to take action at any minute!
- be prepared and fight against other players. Create a strong army to defend your city and to be well-protected in battle.
Don’t forget to upgrade your castle. The castle is the core of your kingdom!

GET READY FOR THE CHALLENGE!

* battles and wars with online multiplayer
- you’re not the only one here! There are thousands of players from around the world! And they are ready for any new challenge! Play online PVP against them! It’s time to send your army to take over other cities. YOU WILL BE THE STRONGEST!

* amazing MMO world
You are in a fantasy world where kingdoms and empires fight to take control. equip an army and collect resources.
BE THE LORD OF THE WORLD!

* build strong alliances around the world.
- western kingdoms is an online RTS MMO RPG that puts you in command of an army. Your alliances will help you in your battles and will help them in return. Don’t forget to be prepared for any attack!

* manage your resources and put the best strategy
- a strong army needs food and houses. Build farms and mines to earn resources to strengthen your city and army.
Earn coins for every completed quest and resources from every harvest. Build defenses for your city from your harvest.

* Amazing 3D MMO battles
- Guide your online army in a world rendered in appealing 3D graphics. Watch the battle realistically while arrow shots light up the battlefield.

* The more your empire develops, the more enemies you will have.
- others will try to destroy your city and power. Always be ready for action during the army’s march into battle to defend your land or conquer another player’s land.

ARE YOU READY TO BE THE STRONGEST LORD IN THE WORLD?

Download western kingdoms and enjoy the war!

title: Clash of Kings: معارك الغرب

creator: Vplay Games LTD.
descriptionHtml:
Crush your enemies in online combat and compete in MMO battles in clash of kings
This is the Clash of Kings: Legacy!
a new RTS RPG multiplayer war game that pits your army against friends and enemies all over the world in a battle for towns and cities
Are you strong enough to roll your kingdom and defeat other players worldwide?
It’s time to Proof your strength and abilities!
crush your enemies in online PVP combat and become one of the most potent lords in medival kingdoms!
compete in online MMO battles in a classic clash of kings


Get ready for the challenge!

CLASH OF KINGS: LEGACY FEATURES:

Art of War Strategy Competition
-You can challenge the monster captain with the whole kingdom player and be The best strategy master who gets awards a week.


Build your city and prepare for action
-You never know when you’ll have to battle against other lords. Your town needs to have a strong army and be well-defended in battle. Build your city and upgrade your castle, fortress, hospital, army barracks, and more to defend yourself in PVP multiplayer battles.


Multiplayer PVP war battles online
- You’re not the only person building an empire! Play PVP online against thousands of other players in the best real-time strategy MMO game. Prevent a siege by building up your town. Send out your army to take over other cities. Collect their resources and conquer their empire.


MMO universe with massive online battles
- Enter an amazing online world where kingdoms battle for control of a PVP fantasy world. Tactical MMORPG gameplay has you building a kingdom, customizing your armies, and collecting resources. Role-play your way in this online multiplayer battle game.


Build strong alliances with others
- Build alliances with other lords and leaders around the world. Clash of Kings: The West is an online RTS MMO RPG that designates you as the army’s leader. Join alliances to help yourself and others. Join like-minded army leaders and help each other build cities, upgrade buildings, or battle enemy armies. In this real-time strategy game, your alliances can make or break you.


Real-time strategy and resource management
- A strong army needs food and housing. Build farms and sawmills to gain resources to strengthen your city and your army. Earn coins for every quest completed and resources from every harvest. Build defenses for your city with all of your harvests.


Amazing 3D MMO battles
- Guide your online army across a massive multiplayer world rendered in gorgeous 3D graphics. Watch each battle spring to life as your defenses clash with enemy armies, and each sword swing and arrow shot light up the battlefield.


The bigger you build your empire, the more enemies you create in this RTS PVE and PVP MMO war game


ARE YOU READY TO BE THE STRONGEST LORD IN THE WORLD?


Download Clash of Kings: Legacy and enjoy the war!
descriptionShort: Compete with global strategy lovers in Clash of Kings and fight for a Legacy

creator: Vplay Games.
descriptionHtml:
🔥 Clash of Kings: Legacy 🔥

Lead your kingdom to glory in this epic strategy RPG! Assemble a mighty alliance, recruit legendary warriors like Vikings, and command powerful troops in thrilling battles. Conquer rival kingdoms, explore the abyss of uncharted lands, and dominate the thrones game. Forge your legacy as you embark on quests in a world of war, strategy, and conquest, featuring the exotic kings of the past.

👑 Key Features of Clash of Kings: Legacy 👑

🌍 Global Players: Join forces with millions of players worldwide in real-time battles. Form alliances, strategize, and clash with rival lords across the kingdom and kingdom empire.

⚔️ Heroes & Commanders: Recruit legendary warriors, Vikings, and barbarians as your commanders. Customize their abilities and lead your armies in battles against rage game opponents like the war kings and kingdom dominion. Battle for supremacy in this 4X strategy game.

🎮 Stunning 3D Graphics: Immerse yourself in a visually captivating world. Witness battles that resemble epic moments from games if trones as you conquer clash kingdom, castle, and empire kingdoms.

📈 Resource Management: Gather resources, upgrade buildings, and expand your empire. Balance economy and military might as you rise to power in the age of kingdom and world of kings.

🏆 Thrilling Campaigns: Embark on heroic quests in the crusade for dominance. Defeat enemies in the clash of worlds and earn your place among kings and queens in kings battle.

👑 Guild Wars & Kingdom vs. Kingdom: Engage in epic guild battles and clash for control of rival kings’ quests. Dominate the royal throne and rule over your enemies in a rage-filled campaign of strategy and civilization.
Enjoy ultimate KvK warzone.

🎲 RPG Elements: Customize your heroes and explore diverse terrains from jungles to castles. Conquer the shadow of the colossus and outwit your enemies in this strategic adventure.

🎉 Events & Domination: Participate in exciting events and conquer new lands. Build your empire, conquer clash titans, and expand your influence in the rise of kingdom and civil wars.

🛡️ Barbarians & Conquest: Defeat barbarian hordes and expand your realm. Prove your strength in battles against monster kings in the kings road, jungle king, and barbarian king campaigns.

🎮 MMO & RTS: Enter an online world where kingdoms battle for control of Middle East lands in PvP combat. Engage in MMORPG gameplay, build your kingdom, and face off against cok enemies while preparing for war against sacramento kings or cavs rivals.

🔨 PvP & Empire: Clash with rival lords in this last war: survival. Defend your clash kings throne and lead the last fortress in this ultimate test of power. Will you rise as the king of kings?

🎯 Art of War Strategy Competition: Compete in the supreme strategy competition alongside your allies in west kingdom. Conquer the battlefield and prove yourself as the best in this epic kings mobile saga.

🎮 Rise of Kings: From the skyward battles to the clash of kings with cash kings, every move counts as you strive to take control. Fight against godzill-sized enemies and kingsman rivals to secure your kingdom's future.

🌟 World of Kings: Embark on a journey across the king city, face clash for clans battles, and test your might against the ultimate enemies. Stand tall as the dragon king of kings cross and claim the king’s road.

🌍 Empire Kingdoms & Thrones: With every battle, you’ll rewrite history in the empire kingdoms saga. Crush your foes and lead your realm to become the most dominant in the kings game. Play kings and prove that you are the ultimate ruler.
descriptionShort: Clash of Kings: Epic wars with warriors, vikings, dragons, and castle conquests!
